        <section id="philosophy">
            <h1>Philosophy</h1>
            <ul>
                <li>Full support for HTML elements (and only HTML elements)</li>
                <li>Smart CSS rules for good out-of-the-box layouts</li>
                <li>Wide support for base colors and patterns</li>
                <li>Opinionated but simple design rules</li>
                <li>Easy to overwrite when everything goes horribly wrong</li>
                <li>No grid, no columns, no components</li>
                <li>There are no ugly colors, only ugly color schemes</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

